Overview

[Psa 141:1](../../../bib/kjv/psa141.htm#001.md), David prays that his suit
may be acceptable; [Psa 141:3](../../../bib/kjv/psa141.htm#003.md), his
conscience sincere; [Psa 141:7](../../../bib/kjv/psa141.htm#007.md), and
his life free from snares.

